*.nupkg
*.snupkg
# NuGet Restore
node_modules/
packages/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## [Operating System]
# Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

## [Project-specific]
# Backup and temp files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.swp
*~

## [User-specific settings]
.vs/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.user
*.userprefs
*.v12.suo
*.v11.suo
*.v10.suo

## [Common logs]
*.log
